<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;"><%= @template_params[:ao_name] %>,</h2>
    <h2 style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;">You have been allocated the PQ <%= @template_params[:uin] %></h2>

    <div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; padding-left:0.5em;margin-left:10px;border-left:2px solid grey;margin-top:5px;margin-right:5px;margin-bottom:5px;">
      <%= @template_params[:question] %>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Asked by: <%= @template_params[:member_name] %> (<%= @template_params[:house] %>)</p>
    <div style="padding-left:0.5em;margin-left:10px;border-left:2px solid black;margin-top:5px;margin-right:5px;margin-bottom:5px;">
        <div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">
          You need to <%= link_to "accept or reject this question", controller: "assignment", action: "index", uin: @template_params[:uin], token: @template_params[:token], entity: @template_params[:entity], :host => root_url %> before <strong>2pm today.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">If you accept the question, you will be sent a further email with all the relevant guidance to draft an answer.</p>
    <p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">If you have any queries please <a href="mailto:pqs@justice.gsi.gov.uk">contact the PQ Team</a></p>

    <%= render 'shared/mailer/email_signature' %>

  </body>
</html>